doctype html
html
  head
    title Verification Successful
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333333;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 500px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #4152b3;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555555;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .highlight {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #4152b3;
        margin-top: 20px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      ul {
        text-align: left;
        margin: 15px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: #555555;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      ul li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: #28a745;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
  body
    .container
      .success-icon ✅
      h1 Email Verified Successfully!
      p Thank you for verifying your email. Your account is now fully activated, and you're all set to enjoy the features we offer. Here’s what you can do next:
      ul
        li Explore your account and update your profile.
        li Start shopping and discover exclusive deals tailored for you.
        li Access your order history and manage your wishlist seamlessly.
      p If you have any questions or face any issues, feel free to contact our support team. We're here to help!
